divs: Sighting DetailsI walked out of the bar to go home, I looked up & saw three lights in the sky. Someone said "whats that?". I said "I dont know" several of us stood there & wathed it. I kept taking pictures other ppl were taking pictures too. The lights moved seemingly independent of eash other. Two lights faded away one stayed longer. as the other light was moving away, a small airplane flew into that airspace (so it seemed to me). after it was over I definately felt that i had seen something strange.
trends: There have been no other sightings in Darlington

Summary: three white lights in the shape of a triangle moved independently, 2 faded away, one lingered then left.
